patthana8.5:4.1: Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.5:4.2: Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetuvippayutto ceva na nahetu ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.5:4.3: Nahetuñceva nahetuvippayuttañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca nahetuvippayutto ceva na nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. #3

patthana8.5:5.2: Nahetuvippayuttañceva na nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.5:5.3: Nahetuvippayuttañceva na nahetuñca dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ceva nahetuvippayutto ca nahetuvippayutto ceva na nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. #3
